data.description: NEW Roof 2023. NEW HVAC 2023. Welcome to this delightful 2 bedroom, 2 bath home on a great corner lot! Upon entry, you'll be greeted by a cozy living area with wood burning fireplace. The open concept plan makes it great for entertaining. The kitchen has ample cabinet space as well as informal dining space. The Master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an en-suite bath for added privacy. The second bedroom is equally comfortable and is serviced by a well-appointed hallway bathroom. There is a covered back patio and a large yard with a privacy fence. Schedule your private showing before this one is gone!!
